## Introduction

Building real-time applications like chat apps at scale requires careful architectural planning...

### Technologies Used
- Node.js
- Socket.io
- Redis
- MongoDB

### Code Sample

```js
const io = require("socket.io")(server, {
  cors: { origin: "*" }
});
io.on("connection", (socket) => {
  console.log("User connected");
});
```

### Conclusion

You can now scale your app horizontally with Redis pub/sub and Docker orchestration.
